Over the last few years, the Samsung Galaxy has become one of the most popular smartphone devices. A range that comes in almost all shapes and sizes, the Samsung Galaxy Tips, Tricks, Apps & Hacks Volume 2 aims to provide you with an in-depth look at different ways of making your device more personal, making it more security and run as smoothly as possible. As well as looking at the vast numbers of apps and how they can improve your everyday Galaxy usage.
